This software is a GNU Radio Out of Tree module implementing
generinc encoder and decoder for LDPC codes. This module is
developed as part of Google Summer of Code 2013, by Manu T S,
under the mentorship of Dr-Ing. Jens Elsner.

In case of bugs please report with the author. Author can be
contacted through his email.

 - manu.t.sree@gmail.com

-----------------------------------------------------------

        Build Instructions

-----------------------------------------------------------

(A) Using PyBOMBS
-------------------

    This assumes that you have installed GNU Radio using PyBOMBS

    Please get the pybombs recipe from
    - https://github.com/manuts/gr-ldpc/blob/master/gr-ldpc.lwr

    Run ./pybombs install gr-ldpc


(B) Using cmake
-------------------

    Make sure that you have installed GNU Radio
    Run the following commands

      $ mkdir $(builddir)
      $ cd $(builddir)
      $ cmake [OPTIONS] $(srcdir)
      $ make
      $ make test
      $ sudo make install
